Package: rsinaica
Type: Package
Title: Download Data from Mexico's National Air Quality Information System
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(person("Diego", "Valle-Jones", email = "diego@diegovalle.net", role = c("aut", "cre")))
Description: Ready-made functions for downloading air quality data from the 
    Mexican National Air Quality Information System (SINAICA). See 
    <http://http://sinaica.inecc.gob.mx> for more information.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/diegovalle/rsinaica
BugReports: https://github.com/diegovalle/rsinaica/issues
